<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-national-authority-for-counter-eavesdropping> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The UK National Authority for Counter Eavesdropping (UK NACE) protects national security by providing Technical Security expertise to the government and the critical national infrastructure (CNI). We provide leadership for the technical security profession across government. UK NACE is part of the FCDO Services ."@en .
